metadata.name: MiM
metadata.description:
When his life was ruined, his family killed, his farm destroyed, Job knelt down on the ground and yelled up to the heavens, "Why god? Why me?" and the thundering voice of God answered, "There's just something about you that pisses me off." Mim. Is said to be the name of god in Judaism and Islam. Aleph, Mim and Laam will be 3 paintings in the same category. searching for the true meaning of life.

*acrylic on canvas. banned by OS, burned and reminted on DystopiansXII custom contract by the artist as a protest.
